{
  "stem": "17867.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was smoke.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The barn was on fire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember that I didn't want to get up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was the first time I had something that was a little bit better than that terrible hole.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She says, the place is on fire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We have to get out of here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we couldn't go down because everything was burning so much there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But there was, like, a little doorway or a little window up on the top.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And she opened it up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she said, you hold my hand because we're going to jump.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I says, well, I'm afraid to jump.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She says, we have to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We have to jump or get burned alive in this place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we jumped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know it's amazing-- didn't break a leg, didn't break an arm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's like somebody was looking over us-- and continued to run.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, like, my whole childhood, that's all I knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know from being a child-- constant fear, constant hunger, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] thirst.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We woke up, and it was burning, burning so much-- so much fire.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just going right up-- the straw and the dry wood and everything was just-- [POINTS].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We kept on running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were in-- hiding behind cemetery places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told you about the, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the, the place where the corn-- tall corn grows.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were hiding in places like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then the Germans got on to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They started finding a lot of them in these places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they started looking in these places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I'm talking now-- it doesn't seem like I was the one going through it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
